title: Philips Hue - Late Night Light
description:
Get up without waking up.

With Philips Hue, getting up at night doesn’t mean waking up at night.

Philips Hue helps you with every aspect of your lighting.
For example, you can ensure that a hallway or bedroom light during a night-time bathroom visit doesn’t disturb anyone’s sleep, and that includes yours. No fumbling for light switches. The Hue motion sensor detects where, when and what light you’ll need. So you can keep dreaming as soon as you’re back in bed.

title: How To - Cara Instal Starter Kit Philips Hue
description:
Create your personal wireless lighting system with Philips Hue. Get started by installing a Philips Hue starter kit in a few easy steps. 

With Philips Hue you can easily control your light from your device, with smart accessories or even with your voice. Create your ambiance for every moment and change the way you use light. Learn more about Philips Hue with this series of how to videos. This video explains how you can easily install your Philips Hue starter kit in a few simple steps. It only takes a few minutes to set up the bridge, connect the lights and control them with the Philips Hue app.
